column5: I found some good deals at cabelas.ca recently...did a big order on snow camo/bunch of other small things and shipping was only 23 bucks and arrived in 5 business days...hope this ain't considered spam, just thought I'd share, very good deal on a calcutta, if only they were lefties for me  http://www.cabelas.ca/index.cfm?pageID=69&&SrchSection=1188&ID=5113
